{"tid":591473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★Apple已死！調查顯示，僅22%現有iPhone用戶打算在今年換新型號","createTime":"2018-03-13T14:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T14:46:42.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a9a1a767503319d61f1efba7a03937d7be36f248","tid":591473,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T14:30:17.000Z","msg":"外媒報道，Loup Ventures對美國消費者進行了一次調查，以了解他們中有多少人會在今年秋天購買新型號的iPhone。結果顯示，今年秋天iPhone的增長將會放緩。<br />\n<br />\nLoup Ventures在美國的問卷調查顯示，<span style=\"color: red;\">僅22%現有iPhone用戶</span>打算在今年秋天蘋果推出新型號時購買新手機。但另一方面，有意在未來一年內購買蘋果此前推出的iPhone X或是iPhone 8/Plus的受訪者則佔20%。<br />\n<br />\n在去年的同類調查中，有23%的iPhone用戶計劃購買新型號(即iPhone 8系列及iPhone X)。Loup Ventures認為，消費者對於新型號的iPhone需求已經放緩。綜合前兩年的數據來看，iPhone的出貨增長率將在1%至5%之間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180313/bkn-20180313202212588-0313_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180313%2Fbkn-20180313202212588-0313_00842_001.html&d=2awl7aVtIIn4Kw4zsVcm1bIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=ee686254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180313/bkn-20180313202212588-0313_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b3b4fb863602943d74f056d4a98daa0b21fd21bf","tid":591473,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T14:31:00.000Z","msg":"all strong hold old model<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c288cc7f56df1ee8f3fbee4ebaa06012312a98fe","tid":591473,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T14:34:52.000Z","msg":"Apple 已死，執笠可期 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8d389b77f62f76bc542c209cb54244db4ee025","tid":591473,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c288cc7f56df1ee8f3fbee4eb